data.text:
For years, you’ve known us for our expertise in ultrasound technology. What you might not know is that we uphold the same standards of excellence in all aspects of Diagnostic Imaging. From X-rays to MRIs, we focus on providing you with the solutions you need to deliver compassionate, high-quality care. Learn more about what Probo can offer you here: https://lnkd.in/dBdzC5-J

Exciting News from DirectMed Imaging! We are thrilled to share that Titanium Medical Imaging is now part of the DirectMed Imaging family. Experts in Canon/Toshiba parts, systems, and service, Titanium Medical brings over 30 years of OEM expertise to the DirectMed team. Titanium has approximately 10,000 parts in stock allowing us to now provide our customers with mission critical parts for their Toshiba and Canon systems. Please join us in welcoming Titanium Medical Imaging to the DirectMed family! And please click here https://hubs.li/Q02p64fL0 to read more about this fortunate milestone for our company. DirectMed: Comprehensive made simple.

Less than 25 days until RSNA 2023 in Chicago! We have some big news to share at the event. Eagerly awaiting the top radiology event of the year. Ready to dive into the latest innovations and connect with industry peers. Who's joining? Let's meet up! ✔️ Parts for MRI, CT, and more ✔️ Imaging Systems ✔️ MRI Coil Repairs ✔️ Radiology Service Training
